{"tid":2417952,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"與MOMO公開戀愛逾1年　金希澈自爆：被逼今年要結婚","createTime":"2021-02-22T08:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T05:20:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":68,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6294c4313da7bd35e5610299d37a908aca44a4","tid":2417952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"南韓天團super junior成員金希澈於2020年初認愛twice成員momo，兩人成為2020年第一對藝人情侶，粉絲們也相當看好兩人的戀情，紛紛給予真誠的祝福，而希澈近日在節目上透露已經39歲的他開始被媽媽催婚，希望他能夠在今年完成婚姻大事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/08/06/2057484-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F2057484-PH.jpg&h=8a688b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈（左）與MOMO去年公開戀愛。（合成圖／翻攝自臉書、IG）<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月時，有韓媒爆料希澈與MOMO早已是戀人關係，且已交往長達2年之久，不過當時雙方皆否認消息，僅說是關係友好的前後輩關係，結果2020年1月1日深夜同一家媒體再度爆料兩人為「戀愛進行式」，這次雙方選擇大方認愛，不過稱兩人是在最近互相有好感，才有了進一步的關係，兩人公開戀愛至今已超過1年。<br />\n<br />\n而希澈在昨（21）日播出的綜藝節目中，詢問一同上節目的裴正男有沒有想結婚的想法，對方當場大方地表示自己希望能夠在45歲左右時結婚，想不到接著希澈便自爆已經39歲的他，近日遭到媽媽逼婚，要求他要在今年完成婚姻大事。<br />\n<br />\n不過希澈接著表示，因為自己一個人過生活實在是太舒服了，所以對於踏入人生的下一個階段還是有點疑慮，金鍾國聽聞後也表示「，如果很享受一個人的生活，那真的出大事了呢」。"},{"pid":"0cf9e6145a343283c2b9c0745227d6cf42c842d6","tid":2417952,"uid":320204,"like":47,"dislike":65,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"金希澈去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d356fec1f6df78b57278aaab5a1de0fe22de66","tid":2417952,"uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":41,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"0cf9e6145a343283c2b9c0745227d6cf42c842d6","tid":2417952,"uid":320204,"like":47,"dislike":65,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"金希澈去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ca22f8b49e2b89c45c8ebac98e5fd8cdacf1c8","tid":2417952,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"中出左"},{"pid":"d6f3e44827b1ea451751b4d4117152e902e08495","tid":2417952,"uid":71657,"like":7,"dislike":63,"score":-56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"IU又食過 Momo又食過<br />\n<br />\n幸福JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27924975f7ad4becb887497ea31a59b477e98a5e","tid":2417952,"uid":224479,"like":21,"dislike":9,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:03:44.000Z","msg":"一晚屌1次 屌左365次 然後話唔想結婚<br />\n佢當momo係啲咩??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281fc7657dd77897955e5ad852c91ba76c9dca67","tid":2417952,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"我想結...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceaf32411ff3108a0650ffb419b8f44f62af008","tid":2417952,"uid":162726,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"金希澈媽媽爆料兒子不打算結婚：他說哥哥們的生活實在太有趣了～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2232513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2232513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6334005989ece3d1777d8207dc63f7c9ca6d8e71","tid":2417952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"281fc7657dd77897955e5ad852c91ba76c9dca67","tid":2417952,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"我想結...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"我結了...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6a9392e61ff9e34c7b144c64242dac82270280","tid":2417952,"uid":274500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"要結婚咁tw